org.switchyard.remote

Class RemoteEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.switchyard.remote.RemoteEndpoint

  • @Strategy(access=FIELD)
public class RemoteEndpoint
extends Object
    Represents a service endpoint registered in a distributed registry.
